To-Do list for new Students

  1. Check in at OISS(Office of International Students and Services)
  2. Get a free sim card in the office of OISS/ order one online
  3. Create a bank account
  4. Get a job on campus by contacting the hiring manager
  5. Call(800) 447-3333 to make an electricity account & transfer it to your name
  6. Contact any fellow brother/sister before making any important decision, they are always willing to help
